data.title: Kevin O'Leary Says Altcoins Not 'Bouncing Back' As Investors Realize Bitcoin And Ethereum Are All You Need In Crypto: 'They Have No Use Case'
data.description: Renowned investor and media personality Kevin O'Leary said Monday that altcoins are no longer bouncing back after market corrections, as investor attention is now solely on Bitcoin (CRYPTO:
